 bytnạ ybqy̱ lyk .. ybqy̱ mḥfwẓ fy ạ̹ydyk
 bytnạ hygẖny lyk
 ạlqrạr- (bytnạ hygẖny lyk)4 .. whyrfʿ lk htạf
