 bytnạ hygẖny lyk
 3- whtskn ʿndnạ .. wạ̉wlạdnạ bʿdnạ
 lyk ysjdwạ wyʿbdwạ .. ḍạmnyn fyk sʿdnạ
 tmlạ ạlbyt ạ̉frạḥ .. tbqy̱ ạ̹nt fyh btrtạḥ
 bytnạ hygẖny lyk</lyrics>
